()Is code ko step-by-step dekh:-
if (admin == null) {
    throw new RuntimeException("Admin not found");
}

🔍 Kya hota hai yaha?
👉 Case 1: admin == null (Condition TRUE)
throw new RuntimeException(...) execute hoga
Exception turant throw ho jayega
Us line ke baad ka code execute nahi hoga
Control current method se bahar chala jayega

👉 Matlab:-
Current method yahi ruk jayega
Aage ka code skip ho jayega.

